# Kopia Ignore Rules
# This file is used by Kopia to exclude files and directories from snapshots.
# The syntax is similar to .gitignore.

# --- General & OS-specific ---
# Windows system files and directories
**/$RECYCLE.BIN/
**/System Volume Information/
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini
pagefile.sys
swapfile.sys

# macOS system files
**/.DS_Store
**/.Spotlight-V100/
**/.Trashes

# Linux/Unix system files
**/.gvfs
**/lost+found/

# --- Development ---
# Node.js
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log
**/yarn-error.log

# Python
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.eggs/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/*.egg-info/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/

# Go
**/vendor/

# Docker
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore

# IDE & Editor specific
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
**/*.sublime-project
**/*.sublime-workspace
**/.history

# --- Common Applications & Caches ---
# General cache folders
**/cache/
**/caches/
**/.cache/

# Dropbox
**/.dropbox
**/.dropbox.cache/

# Google Drive
**/.drive/
**/.drive. কয়েক সেকেন্ডের মধ্যে/

# VirtualBox
**/*.vbox
**/*.vdi
**/*.vmdk
**/*.pvm

# --- Temporary & Log Files ---
**/*.tmp
**/*.temp
**/*.log
**/*.bak
**/*.swp
